Hi {{ fname }},

<p>A new opportunity was just entered that matches the focus(es) and skill(s) you 
    entered. We'd appreciate your feedback on your experience with any opportunity.</p>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td>Nonprofit</td>
            <td>{{ opportunity.nonprofit.orgname }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Name</td>
            <td>{{ opportunity.oppname }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Description</td>
            <td>{{ opportunity.description }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% if opportunity.nonprofit.website is not null %}
            <tr>
                <td>Web site</td>
                <td><a href="{{ opportunity.nonprofit.website }}">{{ opportunity.nonprofit.website }}</a></td>
            </tr>
        {% endif %}
    </table>
<p>Thanks for registering as a volunteer!</p>
<p>The ConnectionsReno Team</p>
